rows.label: qst701404_msg0001
rows.name:
No matter how many we
defeat, there's no end...

rows.label: qst701404_msg0003
rows.name:
If I got serious, I
could probably do it...

rows.label: qst701404_msg0004
rows.name:
Don't. Not a single person
would be able to pass.

rows.label: qst701404_msg0007
rows.name: It was written in my diary...

rows.label: qst701404_msg0008
rows.name:
It seems the Tizza Parisax
has a scent it dislikes.

rows.label: qst701404_msg0012
rows.name:
However, to make Pestronella Oil, we
must first gather the materials.

rows.label: qst701404_msg0013
rows.name:
Adel-sama... Do you know
where Pestronella live?

rows.label: qst701404_msg0014
rows.name:
I believe I've heard that Pestronella
grows in the Verdant Fairylands.

rows.label: qst701404_msg0016
rows.name:
First, we'll gather the Pestronella,
then have Kagutsuchi make it...

rows.label: qst701404_msg0017
rows.name: Then we'll come back here and test it.
